# Week 01 - Cloud Fundamentals & AWS Introduction

## Learning Objectives

- Understand fundamental concepts of Cloud Computing.
- Explore AWS ecosystem and service categories.
- Setup AWS learning environment.

## Activities

Studied:

- Cloud Computing concepts.
- Cloud deployment models.
- Service models:
  - IaaS
  - PaaS
  - SaaS

Explored AWS services:

- Amazon EC2
- Amazon S3
- Amazon RDS
- IAM

## Key Outcomes

- Understand basic cloud concepts.
- Become familiar with AWS Management Console.
- Understand the role of cloud computing in enterprise systems.
